fields.body: Well, I'm a little biased I guess
I've always wanted to comment on pictures. Now I can with readrboard.com
Only connect with Facebook? Could you add another option?
It's the funniest way to say hello!
no readrboard icons pop up when you highlight across paragraphs
Love seeing other reader's thoughts using Readrboard.
Michael, thanks -- that is actually by design - for technical reasons, and also, to encourage reactions to stay more focused.
Apple offers $76 billion cash to buy Readrboard.  Readrboard says no, waiting for better deal.  Hires Jerry Yang as strategic consultant.
That is a face that will sell millions!!!
Love the voice in the video! Quite charming.
My dog is better looking and should be featured here!
Yeah, cats > dogs when lulz are at stake.
i would actually consider this very full-featured so far.  it's got a lot of stuff in the beta!
how can I see other custom tags people have added?
of the old joke about going to library after lunch and listen to the readers digest
haha, whoever tagged this "meta" first - nice.  Btw, I also realize we're missing a vote-up/agree button for previous reactions on media - we'll have to get that in.
someone set us up the bomb

Originally from Costa Rica, I have spent the past 30 years in the San Francisco Bay Area, one of the best places anywhere! 
Looking for an excuse for frequent visits to the beaches of Costa Rica, my brother and I started Avantica Technologies, an outsourced product development company with nearshore software development centers in San Jose, Costa Rica and Lima, Peru. 
In my spare time, I'm also a travel advisor (read free advice) to anyone going to Costa Rica on business or pleasure.
